body:
Looks like GRBL-Advanced expect X axis to move carriage. 
`
if((settings.flags2 & BITFLAG_LATHE_MODE) && gc_block.modal.lathe_mode == LATHE_DIAMETER_MODE)
{
    gc_block.values.xyz[X_AXIS] /= 2.0;
}
`
Usually lathe arranged differently:
![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/38679154/234313529-b988737a-a1c2-4d39-b59c-efe5f38b6ae0.png)
Z axis for carriage(- to chuck, + away from chuck), X axis for cross slide(- to center, + away from center).
